Name: UFO No!
About the game: What would you do in a UFO invasion? How about spacejack a UFO and use their technology against them! Use Space Age power-ups on these uninvited guests to show them who's boss. Go ahead and give them a black hole to suck them into a vortex, or just nuke 'em to send them back to the Stone Age! Power-ups include health, speed and weapon upgrades, black holes, nukes, slow-mo, and invincibility. FEATURES - 49 Stages of Intensifying Action. - Waves of Space Aliens. - Power-ups. - Swarm Time. - Asteroid Alerts. - Gamepad Support. So what are you waiting for? Download the game now and save our planet!
